        "category": "defensive",
        "description": {
          "value": "<p><strong>The artifact.</strong> Regeneration 20 (suppressed only by <em>Serithtial</em>); <em>mirror image</em> at will; <em>dominate</em> 3/day (@Check[type:will|dc:42]); true seeing; her death is impossible while she wears it — <strong>sundering the Crown with Serithtial</strong> (Hardness 20, HP 80 vs. that blade alone) ends the regeneration and the second soul. <em>Susceptible to Serithtial:</em> each hit from it, @Check[type:fortitude|dc:35] or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.4D2KBtexWXa6oUMR]{Drained 1} (cumulative).</p>"
